<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Crear Materia</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tabler/icons@latest/tabler-icons.min.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50">
    <div class="min-h-screen p-4">
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            
            <div class="mb-8">
                <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Crear Nueva Materia</h1>
                <p class="text-gray-600">Completa el formulario para registrar una materia en el sistema</p>
            </div>

            {{#successMessage}}
            <div class="bg-green-100 border border-green-400 text-green-700 px-4 py-3 rounded-lg mb-4" role="alert">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <i class="ti ti-check text-xl"></i>
                    <span>{{successMessage}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            {{/successMessage}}

            {{#errorMessage}}
            <div class="bg-red-100 border border-red-400 text-red-700 px-4 py-3 rounded-lg mb-4" role="alert">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <i class="ti ti-alert-circle text-xl"></i>
                    <span>{{errorMessage}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            {{/errorMessage}}

            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow border border-gray-200 p-8">
                <form action="/materias/create" method="post" class="space-y-6">
                    
                    <div>
                        <label for="nombre" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">
                            <i class="ti ti-book text-blue-600 mr-1"></i>
                            Nombre de la Materia
                        </label>
                        <input 
                            type="text" 
                            id="nombre" 
                            name="nombre" 
                            required
                            placeholder="Ej: Análisis Matemático I"
                            class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent transition"
                        >
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Campo requerido</p>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <label for="codigo" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">
                            <i class="ti ti-barcode text-blue-600 mr-1"></i>
                            Código de Materia
                        </label>
                        <input 
                            type="text" 
                            id="codigo" 
                            name="codigo" 
                            required
                            placeholder="Ej: MAT101"
                            class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent transition"
                        >
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Debe ser identificable y único</p>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <label for="plan_de_estudio_id" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">
                            <i class="ti ti-certificate text-blue-600 mr-1"></i>
                            Plan de Estudio Asociado
                        </label>
                        <select 
                            id="plan_de_estudio_id" 
                            name="plan_de_estudio_id" 
                            required
                            class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg bg-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent transition"
                        >
                            <option value="" disabled selected>Seleccioná un plan...</option>
                            
                            {{#planes}}
                            <option value="{{id}}">Plan Año {{anio_vigencia}} (ID: {{id}})</option>
                            {{/planes}}
                            
                        </select>
                        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">Requisito de integridad referencial de la materia</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex gap-3 pt-4">
                        <button 
                            type="submit" 
                            class="flex-1 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition font-medium"
                        >
                            <i class="ti ti-check"></i>
                            Crear Materia
                        </button>
                        <a 
                            href="/dashboard" 
                            class="flex-1 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-gray-200 text-gray-800 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-300 transition font-medium"
                        >
                            <i class="ti ti-x"></i>
                            Cancelar
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-6 bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-4">
                <div class="flex gap-3">
                    <i class="ti ti-info-circle text-blue-600 text-xl flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i>
                    <div class="text-sm text-blue-800">
                        <p class="font-semibold mb-1">Nota técnica:</p>
                        <p>Al guardar, el sistema validará de manera automática que el código no esté duplicado y vinculará la materia al modelo relacional correspondiente.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>